WEBVTT

00:15.460 --> 00:19.960
♪During the dark night♪

00:20.100 --> 00:22.750
♪A guiding light♪

00:23.260 --> 00:25.050
♪Just like you♪

00:25.460 --> 00:29.750
♪Makes life turn bright♪

00:30.330 --> 00:35.180
♪Breaking free from darkness♪

00:35.400 --> 00:38.880
♪You gave me strength♪

00:39.230 --> 00:41.780
♪Running for truth♪

00:41.800 --> 00:45.850
♪I find my path♪

00:46.600 --> 00:50.580
♪Drawing on the hope♪

00:51.200 --> 00:54.580
♪That you render me♪

00:55.130 --> 00:58.010
♪In this long journey♪

00:58.260 --> 01:01.680
♪I run on lightly♪

01:19.180 --> 01:22.980
[Reborn]
[Adapted from Qiang Yu's work, Reborn]

01:24.650 --> 01:26.020
Qiao Beiyu didn't die of the disease.

01:26.020 --> 01:26.810
She committed suicide.

01:28.940 --> 01:30.100
She found out about her illness early

01:30.100 --> 01:31.460
and had taken medication regularly.

01:32.009 --> 01:33.890
She could have lived a long life.

01:34.330 --> 01:36.009
Someone published
her condition and personal information

01:36.009 --> 01:37.009
online.

02:00.860 --> 02:01.330
Hello?

02:01.330 --> 02:03.370
Hello? Beiyu?

02:03.820 --> 02:04.620
Who is this?

02:04.900 --> 02:05.980
Is this Qiao Beiyu?

02:06.410 --> 02:07.010
Hello?

02:07.580 --> 02:08.330
Who is this?

02:08.330 --> 02:09.940
Is this Qiao Beiyu's phone number?

02:09.940 --> 02:10.620
You called the wrong number.

02:10.729 --> 02:11.820
I didn't expect to get through.

02:12.220 --> 02:13.130
Stop calling.

02:13.580 --> 02:14.370
Can you stop calling?

02:14.370 --> 02:16.900
Get Beiyu to answer the phone.
Why did she get sick?

02:17.730 --> 02:19.050
What else do you want?

02:19.579 --> 02:20.650
I beg of you.

02:20.770 --> 02:21.620
I beg of you.

02:22.329 --> 02:24.410
Stop calling, okay?

02:25.260 --> 02:26.300
You're a monster.

02:27.620 --> 02:28.660
Since then on,

02:29.050 --> 02:32.020
she received text messages
and phone calls day and night.

02:33.050 --> 02:34.850
First, hooligans harassed her.

02:35.490 --> 02:38.100
Then, self-righteous strangers,

02:38.100 --> 02:40.180
who felt superior,
joined in the humiliation

02:40.180 --> 02:41.130
and belittlement.

02:44.210 --> 02:46.100
She dropped out of Huanzhou Art School.

02:47.100 --> 02:49.210
She eventually left the hospital

02:50.490 --> 02:52.050
on the Chinese New Year's Eve.

03:19.740 --> 03:21.290
Bei.

05:04.830 --> 05:09.600
[Episode 19]
[Beiyu's DV]

05:21.260 --> 05:22.060
She...

05:23.010 --> 05:25.340
She was so timid. Why would she...?

05:31.010 --> 05:32.780
Maybe living

05:34.100 --> 05:36.890
scares Qiao Beiyu more than death.

05:42.020 --> 05:44.780
Now I understand why our parents think

05:44.980 --> 05:46.850
that settling it peacefully
and hiding the truth

05:46.850 --> 05:48.490
is the best way to protect us.

05:51.580 --> 05:53.700
It's because words
really can kill people.

05:55.340 --> 05:57.580
It killed Qiao Beiyu
in front of Mom and Dad.

06:01.540 --> 06:04.460
I must find the one
who spread the rumor.

06:04.460 --> 06:07.580
They are the final blow
that destroyed Beiyu.

06:11.250 --> 06:11.810
Everyone.

06:11.810 --> 06:13.250
I have something to say
before school is dismissed.

06:13.610 --> 06:15.050
The NCEE is the day after tomorrow.

06:15.050 --> 06:16.220
Our school is a testing center,

06:16.220 --> 06:17.460
so everyone must

06:17.460 --> 06:19.170
keep the classroom clean before leaving.

06:19.170 --> 06:19.730
Is that clear?

06:19.730 --> 06:20.540
- Yes.
- Yes.

06:20.540 --> 06:22.460
Take home the clutter

06:22.460 --> 06:23.140
in your drawers

06:23.140 --> 06:24.220
or throw it away.

06:24.370 --> 06:25.170
Also,

06:25.610 --> 06:28.610
Get rid of all the notes

06:28.900 --> 06:30.140
on your table.

06:30.410 --> 06:32.100
Sir, what notes?

06:32.140 --> 06:33.220
Don't wrongly accuse us.

06:33.540 --> 06:34.340
Ye Zilin.

06:34.810 --> 06:35.930
Do you think I didn't see
the chemical formulas

06:35.930 --> 06:36.980
on your table?

06:37.370 --> 06:38.659
I didn't say anything

06:38.659 --> 06:40.340
because I was trying to go easy on you.

06:40.340 --> 06:41.140
Anyway,

06:41.490 --> 06:43.100
clean your tables.

06:43.370 --> 06:44.700
Class Monitor,
check the tables after that.

06:44.810 --> 06:46.220
Yes, sir.

06:52.460 --> 06:53.250
Qingyu.

07:06.930 --> 07:08.930
Here are the key points of NCEE
that I've summarized.

07:09.540 --> 07:10.610
Are they all for me?

07:10.850 --> 07:11.850
Take it.

07:11.850 --> 07:13.050
I'm taking NCEE the day after tomorrow.

07:13.050 --> 07:14.250
I don't need them anymore.

07:14.900 --> 07:16.100
Take your time to go through them.

07:16.810 --> 07:17.610
Thank you.

07:24.850 --> 07:25.660
Qingyu.

07:28.490 --> 07:30.100
I decided to treat my dad.

07:33.780 --> 07:35.610
I borrowed money from my aunts

07:35.980 --> 07:36.930
and wrote an IOU.

07:37.460 --> 07:38.540
The total is 200 thousand yuan.

07:41.100 --> 07:42.370
Have you thought it through?

07:42.900 --> 07:43.490
Yeah.

07:44.730 --> 07:45.700
I didn't do it

07:45.850 --> 07:47.700
because of the rumors.

07:48.409 --> 07:49.490
It's because I realize

07:52.490 --> 07:53.900
I love my dad.

07:58.220 --> 07:59.250
I want to save him.

08:00.140 --> 08:01.220
I don't want to regret it.

08:03.980 --> 08:05.610
Will your mom
approve you borrowing money

08:05.900 --> 08:07.290
to treat your dad?

08:09.580 --> 08:11.170
I think my mom

08:11.250 --> 08:12.780
isn't worried about the money.

08:13.610 --> 08:14.980
She just doesn't want it
to drag me down.

08:19.250 --> 08:22.660
If she was sick,

08:23.780 --> 08:25.660
she would also give up treatment.

08:26.980 --> 08:27.780
Qingyu.

08:28.370 --> 08:32.490
I have always envied you and Ming Sheng.

08:37.220 --> 08:40.809
You have the courage
to challenge the world

08:41.340 --> 08:43.020
and the responsibility
to face the consequences.

08:46.540 --> 08:47.540
From now on,

08:48.020 --> 08:50.290
I also want

08:50.410 --> 08:51.460
to be brave and responsible.

09:14.490 --> 09:16.170
Mom.

09:16.930 --> 09:17.580
Hey.

09:17.810 --> 09:19.490
Mom, what happened to your foot?

09:19.490 --> 09:20.730
Nothing. I just sprained it.

09:25.490 --> 09:26.290
Qingyu.

09:26.610 --> 09:29.580
Your mom came to the hospital
to visit mine.

09:30.410 --> 09:31.610
She told my mom about the past

09:32.140 --> 09:33.780
to comfort her.

09:35.340 --> 09:37.930
She said she nearly jumped out
of the hospital window

09:38.410 --> 09:40.810
after your sister died.

09:40.850 --> 09:42.460
It's just a minor sprain.

09:43.730 --> 09:46.410
Fortunately,
the two nurses passing by stopped her.

09:47.290 --> 09:48.340
Come on.

09:48.850 --> 09:49.660
Come on.

09:49.850 --> 09:50.660
Let me do it.

09:52.730 --> 09:53.580
You can't...

09:53.580 --> 09:54.610
Can you carry me?

09:54.730 --> 09:55.980
I'm all grown up.

09:58.730 --> 09:59.420
Sure.

10:00.100 --> 10:00.890
There are a lot of cars.

10:01.700 --> 10:05.300
She also said
if it wasn't for you and your brother,

10:05.650 --> 10:06.980
she would have died
with Qiao Beiyu long ago.

10:06.980 --> 10:07.460
Sit tight.

10:07.460 --> 10:08.650
Be careful. There are a lot of cars.

10:09.940 --> 10:10.730
Qingyu.

10:11.060 --> 10:14.010
I think you may have
misunderstood your mom.

10:15.650 --> 10:19.130
I think your mom
loves your sister very much.

10:20.530 --> 10:23.180
Sometimes, parents' love

10:24.530 --> 10:25.610
runs deep and unspoken.

10:37.010 --> 10:38.770
Do your homework right after dinner.

10:40.940 --> 10:43.010
You don't need to do the dishes.
Just put them in the sink.

10:43.010 --> 10:44.460
I'll clean up when I get back at night.

10:45.370 --> 10:48.100
Mom, you've said it many times.

10:50.530 --> 10:51.340
Ah.

10:58.610 --> 10:59.940
I'm heading back to the shop.

11:05.180 --> 11:06.100
Keys.

11:09.100 --> 11:09.890
They're here.

11:13.250 --> 11:13.890
Oh.

11:19.650 --> 11:22.100
Mom, you don't need
to send me food anymore.

11:22.130 --> 11:23.220
I can cook.

11:23.580 --> 11:25.180
And I don't need rides
to and from school either.

11:25.940 --> 11:26.850
If you're worried,

11:26.850 --> 11:28.180
just call

11:28.250 --> 11:29.420
to check if I'm home on time.

11:31.650 --> 11:33.180
I was ignorant before,

11:33.980 --> 11:35.420
but I won't let you worry anymore.

11:54.500 --> 11:59.180
[Qiao's Handmade Noodle House]

12:14.180 --> 12:16.490
I think what Qing said makes sense.

12:17.220 --> 12:18.850
The restaurant is busy,

12:19.250 --> 12:20.340
and you're still doing
the school drop-offs and pick-ups?

12:20.770 --> 12:21.730
That's a lot.

12:23.010 --> 12:24.300
Yeah, Aunt Fanghao.

12:25.370 --> 12:27.650
It's been a while
since Jinrui's incident.

12:27.730 --> 12:29.340
Qing has learned her lesson.

12:29.580 --> 12:30.650
Didn't you say she improved

12:30.650 --> 12:32.300
on her midterm exam?

12:42.890 --> 12:44.460
Hello? Qiao's Noodle House.

12:50.610 --> 12:51.770
I got a call from hometown

12:52.100 --> 12:54.010
saying Grandpa fell
while going to the bathroom

12:54.010 --> 12:54.890
in the middle of the night.

12:54.890 --> 12:56.130
He can't even stand up.

12:56.700 --> 12:58.340
They could use some help now.

12:58.460 --> 13:00.770
So your mom is going back to help.

13:02.250 --> 13:03.650
Mom is still sick.

13:03.650 --> 13:04.940
How can you let one patient

13:04.940 --> 13:06.060
take care of another?

13:06.220 --> 13:07.060
Who's sick?

13:07.820 --> 13:08.610
I'm not sick.

13:09.060 --> 13:10.460
I put the money in the small bag.

13:11.610 --> 13:13.460
Wasn't it agreed

13:13.650 --> 13:15.850
that Grandpa and Grandma's old house
belonged to Uncle Haisheng and the rest?

13:15.850 --> 13:17.770
Uncle Haisheng will take care of them.

13:17.980 --> 13:20.370
We and Uncle Jiangsheng
will take care of the expenses.

13:20.850 --> 13:22.820
Why are we doing everything now?

13:23.130 --> 13:25.100
There are some things
you kids don't understand.

13:25.340 --> 13:27.340
How can we
be so particular with our family?

13:27.940 --> 13:29.220
If you want to be specific,

13:30.610 --> 13:32.420
you made such a fuss

13:32.610 --> 13:34.730
that Jinrui lost his job.

13:34.730 --> 13:36.490
Frankly speaking, we owe it to them.

13:37.650 --> 13:38.580
I just think

13:38.580 --> 13:40.420
it's a little inappropriate
if you don't go back.

13:40.580 --> 13:42.180
Besides, Grandpa and Grandma also said

13:42.180 --> 13:44.010
they feel sorry for us.

13:44.010 --> 13:44.890
We're a family.

13:44.890 --> 13:46.250
We're related by blood after all.

13:47.420 --> 13:48.890
Our family root lies in Nanqiao.

13:49.650 --> 13:51.850
Your dad and I will have to settle there
when we're old.

13:57.180 --> 13:59.980
Besides, your sister is there.

14:39.580 --> 14:41.340
You're free now.

14:41.980 --> 14:42.890
No one will

14:42.890 --> 14:44.700
watch you so closely anymore.

14:57.300 --> 14:58.490
Do you think

14:59.100 --> 15:01.770
Nanqiao Village is like a long rope,

15:02.730 --> 15:04.300
always pulling us back

15:04.340 --> 15:05.770
no matter how far

15:06.610 --> 15:08.530
we go?

15:10.300 --> 15:12.180
The harder we try to escape,

15:13.060 --> 15:14.130
the more foolish we seem.

15:18.370 --> 15:19.340
I think

15:21.530 --> 15:22.300
I get it now.

15:47.950 --> 15:59.100
[Qiao's Handmade Noodle House]

16:02.300 --> 16:03.340
I want to add some vinegar.

16:03.340 --> 16:03.980
Let me add it.

16:03.980 --> 16:04.610
- Sure.
- Hmm.

16:05.100 --> 16:05.890
Here, add some too.

16:05.890 --> 16:07.130
Try a different flavor.

16:07.130 --> 16:08.060
Yes.

16:09.650 --> 16:10.490
Have some.

16:10.650 --> 16:11.130
I'll have some.

16:11.130 --> 16:13.010
Qingyu, your mom
has been back in your hometown

16:13.010 --> 16:14.370
for over two months.

16:14.490 --> 16:15.490
Why is she not back yet?

16:15.850 --> 16:17.610
My grandpa's condition remains unstable.

16:17.610 --> 16:18.530
She can't leave.

16:19.180 --> 16:20.610
That's why the elderly

16:20.610 --> 16:21.890
are most afraid of falling.

16:23.130 --> 16:24.340
Have you heard?

16:24.610 --> 16:26.610
Wang passed away last night.

16:29.610 --> 16:30.530
Which Wang?

16:30.650 --> 16:31.730
Wang Mumu's father,

16:32.980 --> 16:35.370
from our neighborhood.

16:36.730 --> 16:39.180
We should cherish our lives

16:39.180 --> 16:40.890
and prioritize our health.

16:42.940 --> 16:44.300
Clean sheets and quilts

16:44.300 --> 16:45.460
are in my room's cupboard.

16:46.420 --> 16:48.530
Unplug the electric mosquito coil
when you wake up in the morning.

16:48.580 --> 16:49.820
Otherwise, it's too dangerous.

16:50.490 --> 16:51.300
Also,

16:51.700 --> 16:53.300
don't set the air conditioning too low.

16:53.490 --> 16:55.180
25 or 26 degrees is fine.

16:55.530 --> 16:56.820
Setting it too low wastes electricity.

16:57.300 --> 16:58.220
Got it, Mom.

16:58.370 --> 16:59.220
I'm hanging up.

17:02.300 --> 17:03.180
Are you done?

17:07.890 --> 17:08.700
Qingyu.

17:08.700 --> 17:11.099
You seem a lot calmer lately,

17:11.420 --> 17:14.339
and you've been extremely patient
and caring to Mom.

17:14.849 --> 17:16.490
Are you an impostor?

17:17.250 --> 17:19.180
What do you think?

17:32.340 --> 17:33.460
It tastes just the same.

17:37.340 --> 17:39.770
When I was little,
my dad would buy me a bottle of this

17:40.340 --> 17:41.650
when he picked me up from school.

17:42.460 --> 17:43.580
My mom wouldn't let me have it.

17:44.940 --> 17:46.530
I only went home after drinking it up.

17:48.250 --> 17:50.730
It's a little secret between me and Dad.

17:51.650 --> 17:52.610
Mom doesn't know about it.

17:57.010 --> 17:57.820
These few days,

17:58.580 --> 18:00.100
I've been going

18:00.300 --> 18:03.490
between the hospital, funeral parlor,

18:03.530 --> 18:04.340
and cemetery.

18:04.850 --> 18:07.130
I just realized
that there are so many things to do

18:07.420 --> 18:08.890
after someone dies.

18:10.610 --> 18:13.530
I went to the police station to cancel
my dad's household registration.

18:14.300 --> 18:15.610
My mom and I

18:16.820 --> 18:19.060
are the only ones
on the household register.

18:24.730 --> 18:26.700
When I was packing last night,

18:28.090 --> 18:28.980
I found out

18:30.220 --> 18:32.530
that my dad had kept the birthday cards
I made for him

18:33.460 --> 18:35.090
when I was a child.

18:36.180 --> 18:37.700
There are seven in total,

18:38.660 --> 18:41.010
from when I was three to nine years old.

18:42.140 --> 18:42.980
Later,

18:43.700 --> 18:45.010
Dad's business failed.

18:45.860 --> 18:49.010
My family's life changed forever.

18:53.010 --> 18:55.220
I looked at the cards and thought

18:57.420 --> 18:59.290
it would be nice

19:00.380 --> 19:02.860
if I could go back to my childhood.

19:10.180 --> 19:10.980
Oh, right.

19:11.380 --> 19:12.530
I forgot to tell you

19:12.620 --> 19:14.490
that I was admitted
to Yanbei University.

19:16.380 --> 19:17.010
Congratulations.

19:28.090 --> 19:31.730
I'm taking my mom to Beining.

19:34.380 --> 19:36.050
I still have some left
from the money I borrowed

19:36.050 --> 19:37.140
to treat my dad's illness.

19:37.290 --> 19:39.620
My aunts said
I don't need to pay them back.

19:40.290 --> 19:42.700
They asked me
to take the money to Beining

19:42.700 --> 19:43.860
and settle down with Mom.

19:45.180 --> 19:46.620
Will you come back?

19:48.250 --> 19:49.290
I don't know.

19:50.330 --> 19:53.330
I have no home in Huanzhou anymore.

20:00.730 --> 20:02.180
What if I miss you?

20:07.460 --> 20:08.980
You can give me a phone call

20:09.220 --> 20:10.490
or write me a letter.

20:11.050 --> 20:11.940
When you graduate,

20:11.940 --> 20:13.330
you can come to Beining to visit me.

20:17.900 --> 20:19.420
I won't forget you.

20:19.700 --> 20:20.940
Neither will you.

20:22.530 --> 20:23.380
I promise.

20:34.660 --> 20:35.460
Qingyu.

20:36.810 --> 20:39.220
I have always admired Ming Sheng.

20:40.700 --> 20:42.570
When I advised you
not to accept Ming Sheng,

20:42.730 --> 20:44.250
I actually had selfish motives.

20:49.770 --> 20:50.620
I know.

20:53.570 --> 20:54.380
Do you?

21:22.140 --> 21:23.090
I'll get off work first.

21:23.090 --> 21:23.940
Thank you.

21:24.330 --> 21:24.620
Bye.

21:26.490 --> 21:27.290
Hong.

21:27.490 --> 21:28.290
I'm getting off work.

21:28.290 --> 21:28.980
Okay, bye.

21:29.140 --> 21:29.700
Bye.

21:31.290 --> 21:32.220
Oh, right.

21:33.940 --> 21:34.490
Wang.

21:34.940 --> 21:37.730
The elderly in Bed Six
has been unsupervised.

21:37.730 --> 21:39.090
Ask the caretaker station

21:39.090 --> 21:40.180
when they can send someone over.

21:40.180 --> 21:40.730
Okay.

21:40.730 --> 21:41.810
Sorry to trouble you.

21:41.940 --> 21:42.730
Yanqiu.

21:43.940 --> 21:45.700
Waiting on your dad again?

21:45.860 --> 21:46.380
Hmm.

21:47.250 --> 21:49.420
I remember
your language class offers housing.

21:49.420 --> 21:51.140
So why have you been coming
to the hospital every day?

21:52.290 --> 21:53.570
It's because my dad

21:53.570 --> 21:54.660
is the only one at home.

21:55.010 --> 21:57.730
I'm showing my care
to this old man living alone.

21:58.530 --> 21:59.530
Has Yanqiu left?

21:59.620 --> 22:00.490
She seems to have just left.

22:03.570 --> 22:04.220
Ma'am.

22:04.220 --> 22:06.140
Are you introducing someone
to Yanqiu again?

22:06.140 --> 22:06.900
Yeah.

22:06.980 --> 22:09.940
I told her to wait for me.

22:10.420 --> 22:11.050
Madam Zhang.

22:11.700 --> 22:12.460
Ming Sheng.

22:12.660 --> 22:13.940
Did you see Yanqiu?

22:14.140 --> 22:14.940
No.

22:16.090 --> 22:17.730
She bolts whenever I mention

22:17.730 --> 22:19.180
setting her up.

22:19.700 --> 22:20.490
Madam Zhang.

22:20.660 --> 22:23.050
Are these the men
you picked for Yanqiu?

22:23.090 --> 22:23.700
Yeah.

22:24.330 --> 22:24.860
Look.

22:25.860 --> 22:28.010
This one is a top-tier university grad
and civil servant.

22:28.250 --> 22:29.460
So charming and exceptional.

22:29.700 --> 22:30.620
A civil servant?

22:30.620 --> 22:31.180
Yeah.

22:32.860 --> 22:34.140
And this one. Look.

22:34.180 --> 22:35.460
Though he's not so well-educated,

22:35.460 --> 22:37.010
he comes from a family
that was relocated.

22:37.050 --> 22:38.490
They received multiple houses
in compensation.

22:38.490 --> 22:39.570
This one is good-looking.

22:40.420 --> 22:41.570
Is he rich?

22:42.810 --> 22:44.010
And this one.

22:44.420 --> 22:46.420
His parents are university lecturers.

22:46.570 --> 22:47.090
Their family

22:47.090 --> 22:49.010
will get along very well.

22:49.010 --> 22:49.700
Right?

22:49.700 --> 22:50.570
Yes.

22:51.700 --> 22:52.290
And there's...

22:52.290 --> 22:53.010
There's more?

22:54.730 --> 22:56.940
Why am I talking about all this
to someone your age?

22:57.180 --> 22:58.490
I'll find Yanqiu.

22:58.490 --> 22:59.220
Sure.

22:59.220 --> 23:00.140
Madam Zhang, bye.

23:00.140 --> 23:00.940
Bye.

23:03.940 --> 23:04.730
Is she gone?

23:09.050 --> 23:10.010
I was scared to death.

23:10.330 --> 23:11.620
Our head nurse is so terrifying.

23:11.660 --> 23:13.330
Let's go.

23:16.140 --> 23:16.940
Yanqiu.

23:17.460 --> 23:18.770
Why aren't you considering them?

23:18.810 --> 23:20.660
Those men were quite good.

23:21.090 --> 23:22.380
I would be tempted if it were me.

23:22.490 --> 23:23.570
Do you want me to beat you up?

23:25.700 --> 23:27.090
But be honest,

23:27.730 --> 23:28.810
did you refuse to go on blind dates

23:29.140 --> 23:31.140
because you already
have someone you like?

23:32.660 --> 23:33.490
You really do?

23:34.940 --> 23:36.220
Work hard

23:36.490 --> 23:38.180
and get a boyfriend, then.

23:40.010 --> 23:41.010
Love isn't something

23:41.420 --> 23:43.180
one person alone can decide.

23:44.010 --> 23:45.290
You'll get it when you grow up.

23:52.620 --> 23:53.010
Dad.

23:53.010 --> 23:53.570
Hmm?

23:54.810 --> 23:55.570
Why are you here?

23:56.010 --> 23:56.980
Had your meal?

23:57.460 --> 23:58.050
Yes.

24:04.570 --> 24:05.980
I just ran into Madam Zhang

24:06.220 --> 24:09.810
introducing Yanqiu to blind dates.

24:12.010 --> 24:13.050
You have to admit

24:13.380 --> 24:15.700
those guys are pretty impressive.

24:16.180 --> 24:18.490
I think Yanqiu should be interested.

24:22.460 --> 24:24.530
I didn't realize you were so nosy.

24:25.010 --> 24:26.140
How am I nosy?

24:26.140 --> 24:27.330
I'm worried.

24:27.810 --> 24:30.050
Yanqiu is gentle, kind,

24:30.050 --> 24:31.220
and considerate.

24:31.490 --> 24:32.660
What if she is deceived

24:32.660 --> 24:33.700
by those guys?

24:36.460 --> 24:38.460
Are you talking about Fang Yanqiu
whom I know?

24:39.050 --> 24:40.460
Don't change the subject.

24:41.250 --> 24:41.940
Let me ask you.

24:42.490 --> 24:44.730
If Yanqiu really falls for someone else,

24:44.940 --> 24:45.940
what will you do?

24:47.490 --> 24:51.660
If she really has someone she likes,

24:54.050 --> 24:55.140
she will have my blessing.

24:59.700 --> 25:03.300
[Invitation,
Huanzhou, Jiangnan Province]

25:07.220 --> 25:11.050
Huanzhou
Advanced Medical Worker Award Ceremony.

25:16.620 --> 25:19.290
Dad, I'm coming with you.

25:25.140 --> 25:25.620
Here.

25:26.570 --> 25:27.490
It's freshly fried.

25:27.860 --> 25:29.420
Add as much of this as you want.

25:29.420 --> 25:30.140
Hmm.

25:36.810 --> 25:37.900
Oh, that's a lot.

25:39.860 --> 25:40.620
Oh.

25:41.940 --> 25:44.530
Although Shunyun people
can handle spicy food,

25:44.700 --> 25:45.660
you and Bei

25:45.660 --> 25:47.140
are the only ones in our family

25:47.140 --> 25:48.570
who add sugar to chili oil.

25:49.290 --> 25:50.330
And every time...

25:56.980 --> 25:57.700
Just eat.

25:58.220 --> 25:58.770
Dad.

26:01.570 --> 26:03.860
Do you regret sending Qiao Beiyu
back to Nanqiao Village?

26:11.570 --> 26:12.940
We did her wrong.

26:16.330 --> 26:17.490
Go home and do your homework
after you finish eating.

26:17.490 --> 26:19.050
Or your mom is going to call.

26:24.300 --> 26:27.750
[Huanzhou
Advanced Medical Worker Award Ceremony]

26:32.420 --> 26:33.010
Dr. Ming.

26:33.010 --> 26:33.420
Hello.

26:33.420 --> 26:34.290
Why haven't you gone in?

26:34.290 --> 26:35.730
Oh, I'm waiting for my son.

26:35.730 --> 26:37.250
Alright, see you later.

26:37.250 --> 26:38.050
Okay.

26:53.460 --> 26:54.220
Where's Ming Sheng?

26:56.250 --> 26:58.660
Ming Sheng asked me to come,
saying he needs help.

27:09.730 --> 27:10.940
What are you up to?

27:11.460 --> 27:12.220
Matchmaking.

27:12.220 --> 27:12.980
You...

27:13.900 --> 27:15.940
What are you doing?

27:16.050 --> 27:16.860
Come on.

27:17.420 --> 27:19.490
Is your relationship with Yanqiu

27:19.490 --> 27:20.660
really as secret

27:20.660 --> 27:22.010
as you think?

27:22.530 --> 27:24.770
We've broken up.

27:26.570 --> 27:27.330
I know,

27:28.050 --> 27:30.090
but I can tell you still have feelings
for each other.

27:31.140 --> 27:33.530
Dad, you've sacrificed enough

27:33.660 --> 27:35.330
for your career and for me.

27:35.460 --> 27:37.730
It's time
to be honest about your feelings

27:37.730 --> 27:39.050
and find your happiness.

27:39.940 --> 27:41.140
Most importantly,

27:41.140 --> 27:42.980
neither I nor Yanqiu

27:42.980 --> 27:45.250
need your self-righteous self-sacrifice.

27:45.490 --> 27:46.700
Only when you are happy

27:46.700 --> 27:49.620
will those around you be happy.
Got it?

27:49.900 --> 27:51.290
Yeah, okay.

27:52.700 --> 27:54.140
Give the phone to Yanqiu.

27:54.140 --> 27:55.050
I have something to tell her.

27:55.050 --> 27:55.700
Huh?

27:55.900 --> 27:56.700
Hurry.

27:57.010 --> 27:58.530
Okay.

28:05.810 --> 28:06.460
Hello?

28:06.860 --> 28:07.860
Hello? Yanqiu.

28:09.010 --> 28:11.090
I'll leave my reserved
yet passionate dad to you.

28:11.330 --> 28:12.140
Also,

28:12.330 --> 28:13.980
I won't call you by your name anymore.

28:14.050 --> 28:15.250
I'll call you Ms. Fang

28:15.460 --> 28:16.860
so as not to confuse your seniority.

28:16.860 --> 28:17.490
Hey.

28:17.810 --> 28:18.570
I'm hanging up.

28:29.250 --> 28:30.250
Since you're here,

28:30.330 --> 28:32.570
how about you go in with me?

28:34.330 --> 28:35.140
No.

28:35.730 --> 28:36.980
Those inside are all our colleagues.

28:37.140 --> 28:38.770
We see each other all the time.

28:39.380 --> 28:41.010
Besides, they will misunderstand us

28:41.420 --> 28:42.570
if we go in together.

28:59.940 --> 29:01.290
Dr. Ming, please come in.

29:09.280 --> 29:13.220
[Huanzhou Association
of STDs and AIDS Prevention and Control]

29:13.220 --> 29:15.420
Ms. Le Fan, you wanted to see me?

29:16.330 --> 29:18.220
A few days ago, I was sorting out files
at the association

29:18.490 --> 29:20.530
and found Beiyu's DV.

29:21.770 --> 29:23.050
It concerns her privacy,

29:23.050 --> 29:24.530
and I shouldn't be telling you about it.

29:25.250 --> 29:26.770
But having given it a thought,

29:27.860 --> 29:29.250
I decided to give it to you.

30:09.940 --> 30:11.330
My name is Qiao Beiyu.

30:12.140 --> 30:13.660
I'm 22 years old.

30:14.940 --> 30:17.770
I'm HIV-positive.

30:22.490 --> 30:23.700
I heard

30:25.490 --> 30:27.090
that when I was born,

30:27.900 --> 30:30.620
my grandparents
who were waiting outside the ward

30:30.980 --> 30:33.090
returned to Nanqiao Village

30:33.940 --> 30:35.570
without even looking at me

30:35.900 --> 30:37.660
after they found out I was a girl.

30:39.420 --> 30:40.660
Now that I think about it,

30:44.490 --> 30:48.140
maybe I was destined
to disappoint my family

30:49.860 --> 30:52.050
from that moment on.

30:55.800 --> 30:57.860
[Qiao's Handmade Noodle House]

30:57.860 --> 30:59.180
Let's tie your hair up.

30:59.180 --> 30:59.700
Okay.

30:59.700 --> 31:00.730
Okay, don't move.

31:00.810 --> 31:01.940
Your hair is tied up now.

31:02.010 --> 31:04.460
Oh, how beautiful.

31:04.660 --> 31:05.940
Let's tie your hair up.

31:08.530 --> 31:09.900
I lived with my parents

31:11.530 --> 31:13.530
in Shunyun County

31:13.940 --> 31:16.570
until I was six years old.

31:17.730 --> 31:19.090
We didn't have much money,

31:19.570 --> 31:21.810
but as an only child,

31:22.490 --> 31:25.860
I had all my parents' love.

31:27.530 --> 31:29.660
That was

31:31.250 --> 31:33.460
the most carefree time of my life.

31:44.860 --> 31:49.180
Later, Qing was born.

31:51.330 --> 31:52.940
She's also a girl.

31:54.700 --> 31:57.730
My grandparents were afraid
my parents couldn't take care of me,

31:57.860 --> 32:00.570
so they took me back to Nanqiao Village.

32:03.010 --> 32:03.980
Mom!

32:04.290 --> 32:05.250
Mom!

32:08.220 --> 32:09.180
You're coming with your grandma.

32:09.860 --> 32:10.860
There, there.

32:13.980 --> 32:14.900
Don't worry.

32:15.250 --> 32:15.730
Here, come with me.

32:16.250 --> 32:16.770
You're coming with your grandma.

32:17.530 --> 32:18.490
Let's go.

32:18.490 --> 32:21.420
Mom, I don't want to leave!

32:21.420 --> 32:23.140
There, there.

32:23.140 --> 32:26.380
Mom, I don't want to leave!

32:26.380 --> 32:27.570
Let's go.

32:27.570 --> 32:29.460
Mom!

32:29.460 --> 32:30.660
The adults said

32:31.570 --> 32:34.180
I could go back to my parents

32:35.490 --> 32:37.700
once my brother was born.

32:38.460 --> 32:39.460
Throw it.

32:41.460 --> 32:42.420
Where did it go?

32:42.490 --> 32:44.860
I waited.

32:45.900 --> 32:48.050
My younger brother, Yu,
was finally born.

32:51.010 --> 32:52.010
Where did it go?

32:52.530 --> 32:55.010
But my parents didn't
fulfill their promise.

33:01.660 --> 33:03.140
I'm a burden.

33:06.460 --> 33:08.140
I'm not needed.

33:13.810 --> 33:15.140
Except Jinrui.

33:16.660 --> 33:17.250
Do it.

33:17.250 --> 33:18.140
No.

33:18.330 --> 33:19.460
Light it yourself.

33:19.770 --> 33:21.140
Fine, I'll light it.

33:26.140 --> 33:26.940
Wow.

33:27.050 --> 33:28.530
It's so beautiful.

34:07.490 --> 34:08.250
Jinrui.

34:10.530 --> 34:11.330
Bei.

34:13.090 --> 34:14.179
Why are you back here?

34:14.219 --> 34:16.530
I came back for vacation.

34:18.050 --> 34:18.940
What happened to you?

34:19.900 --> 34:21.460
I accidentally injured myself

34:21.620 --> 34:22.730
when cleaning the house just now.

34:23.530 --> 34:24.330
Let me see.

34:24.330 --> 34:24.810
Hey.

34:25.290 --> 34:26.290
Let me see.

34:32.010 --> 34:32.980
I'll help you apply the medicine.

34:44.570 --> 34:45.090
Does it hurt?

34:47.330 --> 34:47.900
No.

35:03.530 --> 35:06.180
I don't know when it started.

35:08.620 --> 35:11.490
All I know
is that Jinrui was my only salvation

35:13.330 --> 35:14.860
in Nanqiao Village.

35:15.580 --> 35:17.660
He was the one closest to me.

35:27.620 --> 35:28.290
Jinrui.

35:29.290 --> 35:30.730
Have you given any thought

35:30.730 --> 35:31.900
to applying for graduate school?

35:32.170 --> 35:33.260
I'll think about it.

35:34.300 --> 35:35.300
You should.

35:35.490 --> 35:36.570
There are two years left.

35:36.860 --> 35:38.740
You can decide on a major later.

35:39.980 --> 35:41.010
By the way, Bei,

35:41.490 --> 35:42.860
after you graduate from art school,

35:42.860 --> 35:44.460
find a job in an art troupe.

35:45.980 --> 35:48.420
Bei's beautiful.
An art troupe will be a good choice.

35:50.380 --> 35:52.460
We're not related by blood,

35:53.210 --> 35:54.300
so I thought

35:55.690 --> 35:58.010
we could love each other

35:59.490 --> 36:01.420
and be together forever.

36:02.340 --> 36:03.980
Hmm, this tastes amazing.

36:05.050 --> 36:06.280
Have some more.

36:15.340 --> 36:19.860
How sad that dreams must always end.

36:27.690 --> 36:30.650
Jinrui left me

36:32.050 --> 36:34.340
and didn't even glance back.

36:35.340 --> 36:36.570
But I don't blame him,

36:38.690 --> 36:42.690
because I know this is my fate.

36:45.260 --> 36:46.690
I don't deserve to be loved.

36:50.610 --> 36:52.260
Sweetheart, are you alone?

36:52.340 --> 36:53.340
Come on, let's grab a bite.

36:53.530 --> 36:54.090
No, thanks.

36:54.090 --> 36:57.420
It's a lonely night, isn't it?

36:57.420 --> 36:59.420
Who are you? What are you trying to do?

36:59.420 --> 37:00.050
Let's get some late-night food.

37:00.050 --> 37:01.780
No, I said no.

37:03.130 --> 37:03.980
Who are you?

37:06.820 --> 37:08.050
You're quite bold.

37:08.130 --> 37:09.380
How dare you cause trouble here?

37:09.860 --> 37:10.530
Scram!

37:14.690 --> 37:15.740
Are you okay, miss?

37:17.340 --> 37:18.130
I'm okay.

37:18.690 --> 37:20.260
Thank you.

37:20.420 --> 37:21.490
Don't mention it.

37:22.820 --> 37:24.090
What's wrong? Did you lose something?

37:24.260 --> 37:27.010
Yes, I think I left my phone in there.

37:27.050 --> 37:27.860
You left it inside?

37:28.090 --> 37:28.460
Yeah.

37:28.610 --> 37:29.780
No worries.

37:30.610 --> 37:32.210
I'll clear the area
and find your phone for you later.

37:32.210 --> 37:33.170
We'll find it.

37:35.420 --> 37:36.780
Did that punk hurt you?

37:44.300 --> 37:45.490
You can't blame him.

37:47.940 --> 37:50.170
You're indeed quite beautiful.

37:52.420 --> 37:53.260
Don't be scared. Let's go.

37:53.460 --> 37:54.210
Let's go find your phone.

37:54.210 --> 37:54.740
Come on. Don't be scared.

37:54.740 --> 37:56.010
That's how it is with people.

37:56.900 --> 37:59.650
The more you want something,
the harder it is to get it.

38:00.570 --> 38:03.900
The less likely you can get it,
the more you want it.

38:06.650 --> 38:07.690
I couldn't figure it out.

38:10.690 --> 38:11.860
What are you doing?

38:12.340 --> 38:13.340
I've made it clear to you.

38:13.340 --> 38:14.780
We've broken up!

38:15.570 --> 38:18.420
I felt like I was stuck in a loop.

38:19.380 --> 38:21.210
I couldn't see any hope.

38:22.740 --> 38:24.010
When I got sick,

38:24.570 --> 38:25.900
I still couldn't figure it out.

38:27.340 --> 38:29.050
When did they say it was appendicitis

38:30.420 --> 38:32.340
when I was hospitalized?

38:34.130 --> 38:36.820
How come I was infected because of him?

38:43.260 --> 38:44.740
I didn't tell anyone.

38:47.490 --> 38:50.050
I was alone and confused
in the hospital.

38:51.610 --> 38:52.820
I thought

38:54.980 --> 38:56.380
that I might as well just die.

38:57.420 --> 38:59.380
But later the school found out

38:59.780 --> 39:01.300
and encouraged me,

39:01.610 --> 39:03.690
which helped me to pull myself together.

39:06.740 --> 39:07.740
Later on,

39:08.860 --> 39:10.260
Mom and Dad found out.

39:11.780 --> 39:12.980
Mom, don't touch me.

39:15.460 --> 39:16.530
Silly girl.

39:18.030 --> 39:21.480
♪If the flowing water could turn back♪

39:22.300 --> 39:26.830
♪Please take me away♪

39:27.350 --> 39:31.280
♪If the flowing water could accept it♪

39:31.830 --> 39:35.650
♪There would be no more worries♪

39:36.730 --> 39:41.180
♪Someone envies you♪

39:41.630 --> 39:45.850
♪For flowing freely♪

39:46.400 --> 39:50.950
♪I want to be like you♪

39:51.400 --> 39:52.860
♪Going wherever I want♪

39:52.860 --> 39:56.340
Mom and Dad closed the noodle house

39:57.530 --> 40:01.260
and left Qing and Yu in Shunyun,

40:01.980 --> 40:04.490
so they could focus entirely on me.

40:05.150 --> 40:07.260
♪If the flowing water were me♪

40:07.260 --> 40:09.010
This is too old-fashioned.

40:10.030 --> 40:13.900
♪It would cry too♪

40:14.420 --> 40:15.010
How much is it?

40:15.010 --> 40:15.690
A hundred yuan.

40:15.740 --> 40:17.050
A hundred yuan for a scarf.

40:17.260 --> 40:19.050
Does it look good? Isn't it too red?

40:19.900 --> 40:20.940
No, it's warm.

40:21.300 --> 40:22.170
You...

40:22.570 --> 40:23.740
Will 80 yuan do?

40:23.740 --> 40:25.300
No, 100 yuan.

40:25.340 --> 40:26.650
You're quite insistent.

40:28.260 --> 40:28.940
It looks good.

40:29.820 --> 40:30.610
Fine.

40:33.490 --> 40:34.740
It looks good, Mom.

40:35.260 --> 40:35.740
It sure does.

40:35.740 --> 40:36.420
Yeah.

40:37.420 --> 40:38.340
Have you paid for it?

40:38.340 --> 40:39.090
Yes.

40:39.130 --> 40:39.490
Well...

40:39.490 --> 40:40.300
It looks good.

40:40.300 --> 40:40.780
Let's go.

40:40.780 --> 40:41.690
How much is it?

40:41.690 --> 40:42.780
Oh, don't worry about it.

40:42.780 --> 40:43.860
Don't worry about it.

40:44.430 --> 40:49.400
♪Someone envies you♪

40:49.820 --> 40:53.780
Sometimes I think being sick
isn't entirely a bad thing.

40:54.550 --> 40:56.090
♪I want to be like you♪

40:56.090 --> 40:59.420
Being in the hospital made me realize

40:59.690 --> 41:01.340
how much love surrounds me.

41:01.650 --> 41:03.130
Mom and Dad's love for me

41:03.780 --> 41:05.690
is just like their love for Qing and Yu.

41:06.940 --> 41:07.860
Have another bite.

41:07.860 --> 41:10.230
♪If the flowing water were me♪

41:10.380 --> 41:11.050
Watch your hair.

41:11.050 --> 41:15.420
♪It would cry too♪

41:15.420 --> 41:16.210
It's yummy.

41:17.650 --> 41:18.300
Mom.

41:18.300 --> 41:19.940
♪If I were the flowing water♪

41:19.940 --> 41:21.860
You've got a lot more gray hair.

41:21.860 --> 41:24.980
♪I wouldn't look back♪

41:27.740 --> 41:29.420
Here, have another sip.

41:33.940 --> 41:35.610
Have the orange
after you finish the soup.

41:36.260 --> 41:37.460
Dr. Le Fan said

41:38.260 --> 41:39.740
I can share this video

41:40.260 --> 41:41.860
with my loved ones

41:42.010 --> 41:43.610
when I'm ready.

41:43.610 --> 41:46.610
♪Someone envies you♪

41:46.610 --> 41:47.690
I think that day

41:48.900 --> 41:50.740
will come soon.

41:50.740 --> 41:52.800
♪For flowing freely♪

41:53.300 --> 41:57.880
♪I want to be like you♪

41:58.350 --> 42:02.350
♪Going wherever I want♪

42:05.430 --> 42:09.000
♪If the flowing water were me♪

42:09.700 --> 42:14.130
♪It would cry too♪

42:14.830 --> 42:19.130
♪If I were the flowing water♪

42:19.530 --> 42:27.980
♪I wouldn't look back♪

42:28.440 --> 42:29.480
[Acquired Immune
Deficiency Syndrome (AIDS)]

42:29.480 --> 42:30.580
[is a major public health issue.]

42:30.580 --> 42:31.490
[Its pathogen
is Human Immunodeficiency Virus (HIV),]

42:31.490 --> 42:31.970
[also known as AIDS virus.]

42:31.970 --> 42:33.360
[China reported 1.29 million people
with HIV by the end of 2023.]

42:33.360 --> 42:34.720
[China's STD and AIDS
Prevention and Control Association]

42:34.720 --> 42:36.250
[actively promotes knowledge
of prevention and self-protection.]

42:36.250 --> 42:37.610
[Let's protect the rights
of those infected and their families,]

42:37.610 --> 42:38.440
[and create a society
free of discrimination.]

43:06.720 --> 43:10.410
♪Perhaps♪

43:10.920 --> 43:16.620
♪The more we care,
the more careful we become♪

43:17.760 --> 43:23.160
♪Counting the distance
that separates us♪

43:24.160 --> 43:29.720
♪A single step,
and we'd be closer still♪

43:35.390 --> 43:39.060
♪In the future♪

43:39.520 --> 43:45.240
♪Time will reveal this secret♪

43:46.740 --> 43:51.810
♪Waiting is a silent promise♪

43:53.060 --> 43:58.220
♪That never expires♪

44:01.820 --> 44:06.290
♪Turns out that what's on my mind♪

44:07.290 --> 44:10.960
♪Is your name♪

44:11.460 --> 44:16.560
♪The only stubbornness in my heart♪

44:17.640 --> 44:20.860
♪At first sight♪

44:21.290 --> 44:24.570
♪The future has been determined♪

44:25.260 --> 44:30.820
♪Dreams began to feel real♪

44:31.920 --> 44:35.460
♪Turns out that what's on your mind♪

44:35.920 --> 44:39.860
♪Is a place♪

44:40.160 --> 44:45.720
♪Where the same story is held dear♪

44:46.390 --> 44:49.760
♪Fortunately, I'm not sensible enough♪

44:50.090 --> 44:53.560
♪Courage wasn't late too♪

44:54.090 --> 45:00.160
♪Only then does time not betray
our acquaintance♪
